{"tid":163474,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"國民老婆變大嬸　新垣結衣捲髮造型超崩壞","createTime":"2017-03-20T04:07:06.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-20T15:23:26.000Z","uid":9573,"like":5,"dislike":31,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ca9d40a30793f8d514a15a5bc4da5641cb49a70c","tid":163474,"uid":9573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T04:07:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://imgapi.nownews.com/?w=640&amp;q=60&amp;src=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nownews.com%2Fec%2Ff0%2Fecf00c6049d9e5a212198fdbc3968a9b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimgapi.nownews.com%2F%3Fw%3D640%26q%3D60%26src%3Dhttp%253A%252F%252Fs.nownews.com%252Fec%252Ff0%252Fecf00c6049d9e5a212198fdbc3968a9b.jpg&h=f0d7ab7d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲新垣結衣廣告新造型，捲髮卻不受網友青睞，被批像大嬸。<br />\n<br />\n日本知名女星新垣結衣以《月薪嬌妻》聲勢再度翻紅，此次為明治巧克力拍攝廣告還大膽挑戰新造型，全新2公升Turbo引擎輸出245ps馬力和35.7kgm扭力，性能表現方面大勝上代。但勇於突破的她，新捲髮造型似乎不受網友青睞，不少網友更崩潰表示女神怎麼變大嬸！<br />\n<img src=\"http://imgapi.nownews.com/?w=720&amp;q=60&amp;src=http://s.nownews.com/media_crop/171146/hash/83/23/832316d780e28136200884fc02f70c1c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimgapi.nownews.com%2F%3Fw%3D720%26q%3D60%26src%3Dhttp%3A%2F%2Fs.nownews.com%2Fmedia_crop%2F171146%2Fhash%2F83%2F23%2F832316d780e28136200884fc02f70c1c.jpg&h=49f72a20&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲新垣結衣新廣告一人飾二角，捲髮造型被網友批超醜。<br />\n<br />\n新垣結衣因《月薪嬌妻》人氣爆紅，有著「國民老婆」的美譽，不僅如此，據日本ORICON網站公布「第10屆理想女友」票選結果，更打敗綾瀨遙，成為冠軍。這次新垣結衣接下明治巧克力廣告，在裡頭一人飾兩角模樣很是可愛，其中﻿角色還突破原本形象，想以捲髮來賣萌，只可惜網友不領這個情，更毒酸今日有微雨短暫見陽光最高氣溫約23度新垣結衣變大嬸，也讓不少鐵粉崩潰表示，真的無法接受這個造型，直呼女神崩壞了！<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/obkUd8gMFgo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FobkUd8gMFgo&d=fuRTyfFj%2BaUlIJflnhZSnwHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=fbb68bdf\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/obkUd8gMFgo</a>"},{"pid":"70edd46f0ad20f24b57b23e1bde51e054e1f4679","tid":163474,"uid":34033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T04:08:45.000Z","msg":"只可惜網友不領這個情，更毒酸今日有微雨短暫見陽光最高氣溫約23度新垣結衣變大嬸"},{"pid":"612055af68785806a6079e7ce11420237330c211","tid":163474,"uid":78411,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T04:09:14.000Z","msg":"此次為明治巧克力拍攝廣告還大膽挑戰新造型，全新2公升Turbo引擎輸出245ps馬力和35.7kgm扭力，性能表現方面大勝上代。"},{"pid":"db579cf783f5721a0d24a8fe987f4b63212ea587","tid":163474,"uid":2022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T04:09:27.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8831ded1cbd015e43bff018b177fef21cdd87ba3","tid":163474,"uid":33427,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T04:12:35.000Z","msg":"屌，無朱千雪"},{"pid":"21082780d097609006cb8443c5089c79f9589fba","tid":163474,"uid":34005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T04:13:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d522f429d7a400177890c0b83d55a9f43ebbb03","tid":163474,"uid":9053,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T04:15:00.000Z","msg":"但仍然好可愛<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/15.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a03a0a0e59efbffccf744aee9a193cea6704449","tid":163474,"uid":80183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T04:19:50.000Z","msg":"G"},{"pid":"39e9293b37ea0bf783ba1d9cd5e30bd86db7542a","tid":163474,"uid":21028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T04:20:00.000Z","msg":"出道十年有多 而家外國先多人識 <br />\nmy boss my hero 之前而家鍾意佢 不過 無恥冇睇 好悶"},{"pid":"b14c8b3470aabe699c931877f7d377bb97fa77b2","tid":163474,"uid":78411,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T04:30:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>出道十年有多 而家外國先多人識 <br />\nmy boss my hero 之前而家鍾意佢 不過 <del>無</del><span style=\"color: red;\">逃</span>恥冇睇 好悶</blockquote><br />\n你係唔係睇錯劇?"},{"pid":"b874151e26f1f6c2f6f91dc196fee343b6d8ae83","tid":163474,"uid":22080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T04:37:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>出道十年有多 而家外國先多人識 <br />\nmy boss my hero 之前而家鍾意佢 不過 <del>無</del>